{"tid":1352502,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"國賊是曹操，非孫權也。禍港主謀是中亂辦，非鄉黑。","createTime":"2019-07-22T19:40:18.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-22T20:18:56.000Z","uid":70493,"like":4,"dislike":15,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"25979e659ebb97484547d143e3979a1b009ff9ab","tid":1352502,"uid":70493,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T19:40:18.000Z","msg":"我知道大家都好嬲琴日元朗恐襲，<br />\n但係國賊係中亂辦呀！<br />\n你如果走去元朗入村打黑，<br />\n就等於劉備唔去打曹操，走去打孫權為關羽報仇。<br />\n你知唔知道，劉備打孫權嘅結果係點呀？<br />\n係全滅呀！<br />\n<br />\n建議下星期繼續攻打中亂辦，<br />\n只有打到佢地成棟大廈爛晒，佢地先肯退讓。<br />\n你去打元朗，就等於送頭，正中政府同班狗嘅下懷。<br />\n明唔明呀？"},{"pid":"8a20ca01bdda5e0af0a05aa90d742d253725b424","tid":1352502,"uid":54046,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T19:41:44.000Z","msg":"你放棄得元屯天嘅手足，下一次俾人放棄就係你嗰區<br />\n而下次你出事俾人放棄嘅人就係你"},{"pid":"a34631c84312827eb532b6b101657005d598e229","tid":1352502,"uid":51250,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T19:41:50.000Z","msg":"打爛中聯辦咪搵個位起過棟"},{"pid":"3e7437b933022bb8612cfa64fcead6d09dca9f20","tid":1352502,"uid":110109,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T19:48:21.000Z","msg":"冇荊州 劉氏都係得個益州疲弊。<br />\n我認為邊度可以為政權帶黎壓力，邊度都可以係戰場。荊州唔係唔打得，但係要有勇有謀地打。"},{"pid":"5c26e2cf87a4ea1e8c646731164826c1f1d4f02a","tid":1352502,"uid":80303,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"8a20ca01bdda5e0af0a05aa90d742d253725b424","tid":1352502,"uid":54046,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T19:41:44.000Z","msg":"你放棄得元屯天嘅手足，下一次俾人放棄就係你嗰區<br />\n而下次你出事俾人放棄嘅人就係你"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T19:48:49.000Z","msg":"入去和理非遊客冇用<br />\n攞刀入去就犯法"},{"pid":"279b4fceeafef216a3a2ce931bbf3d0f593486b0","tid":1352502,"uid":114665,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T19:49:09.000Z","msg":"我地唔入等於向白色恐怖屈服"},{"pid":"24dcb9916083616b2592a236fb97423c6ca4a9a5","tid":1352502,"uid":171273,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T19:52:38.000Z","msg":"放棄元朗=荊州四郡"},{"pid":"80e37a3a34a3befb3d3a8a1f8555f1d245958de4","tid":1352502,"uid":59989,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T19:53:49.000Z","msg":"Why not both <br />\n官商鄉黑警"},{"pid":"39886696ee49a64a955b5c6f9ca41df19eff8330","tid":1352502,"uid":70493,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"279b4fceeafef216a3a2ce931bbf3d0f593486b0","tid":1352502,"uid":114665,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T19:49:09.000Z","msg":"我地唔入等於向白色恐怖屈服"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T20:01:38.000Z","msg":"要打牛屎佬，其實唔應該入村，<br />\n而係再次引佢地出嚟。<br />\n<br />\n假如號召巿民先出去打中亂辦，<br />\n回程再在地鐵打牛屎佬。<br />\n其它巴絲在元朗預備等候，<br />\n到夜晚全部人一齊出動反包圍元朗地鐵，<br />\n咁反而有機會將成班黑仔打沉。"},{"pid":"68f389e4b1512333b6043ad980b8c584fbd01a62","tid":1352502,"uid":158270,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T20:18:06.000Z","msg":"Why not both"},{"pid":"f867d820fa50eabc70c55640cb909e8e734f2af5","tid":1352502,"uid":103230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T20:18:56.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://lih.kg/aatmCiV\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/aatmCiV</a><br />\n<br />\n諗諗呢個問題"}]}